{"word":"H6168 - עָרָה - ʻârâh - aw-raw' - Leave destitute","slug":"H6168","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָרָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻârâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Leave destitute"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05E8;&#x05D4; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>aw-raw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>bare</i>; hence to <i>empty</i>, <i>pour</i> out, <i>demolish: - </i>leave destitute, discover, empty, make naked, pour (out), rase, spread self, uncover."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4626\">H4626</a>, <a href=\"#/H4629\">H4629</a>, <a href=\"#/H4638\">H4638</a>, <a href=\"#/H6169\">H6169</a>, <a href=\"#/H6171\">H6171</a>, <a href=\"#/H6172\">H6172</a>, <a href=\"#/H6181\">H6181</a>, <a href=\"#/H8593\">H8593</a>"}]}